need_mon   [level 5]: turns Need Monitor On/Off

                      syntax: need_mon
                      
add_need            : adds target to Need List
                      no target shows Need List Members
 
                      syntax: add_need <target>
                              add_need
                      
clear_need          : clears target from Need List
                      'all' will clear the whole list
                      
                      syntax: clear_need <target>
                              clear_need all


